<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157141>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Gorytes mikhailovi sp. nov., holotype, female: 1—habitus, dorsolateral view; 2—labels; 3–4—head, frontal view (3), dorsal view (4); 5—mesoscutellum, metanotum and propodeum, dorsolateral view; 6—base of metasoma, ventrolateral view. Scale bar: 2.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5157141/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157145>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–11. Gorytes mikhailovi sp. nov., paratype, male: 7—habitus, lateral view; 8—F1–F6, ventral view; 9–10—head, frontal and dorsal view; 11—metasoma, dorsal view. Scale bar: 2.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5157145/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5157147>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–15. Metasomal base, lateral view (12, 13) and mesoscutellum, metanotum and propodeum, dorsolateral view (14, 15) of Gorytes females: 12—G. mikhailovi sp. nov., paratype; 13—G. pleuripunctatus (A. Costa); 14—G. hebraeus de Beaumont; 15— G. fallax Handlirsch." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5157147/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

